control structures

1.decision makings
  a. if
    SN:

     if condition
       st1
       st2
     end

   ex:  
    a=10
    b=11

    if a>b
      puts "helloo hyderabad"
    end 
    
    if a<b
      puts "helloo secunderabad"
    end



  b. if else
   SN:

    if condition1

      st1
    else

      st2
    end 


   wirte a program to find maxximum of two numbers

   a=10
   b=15
   c=18
   if a>b
     puts "a is maximum in a,b"
     if a>c
       puts "a is maximum in a,b,c"
     end
   else
     puts "b is maximum in a,b"
     if b>c
       puts "c is maximum in a,b,c"
     end 
   end


