  e. nested if
     SN:

      if condition1
         st1
         st2
        if condition2
           st3
           st4
          if condition3
            st5
            st6
          end
        end
      end

    ex:

      a=10
      b=11
      c=5

     if a < b
       puts "one"
       if a>c
          puts "two"
         if c>b
          puts "three"
         end
       end
     end
   
  g. nested if else
